location.fullValue: Monterey II Plan, K. Hovnanian's® Four Seasons at Charlottesville

data.description: Move-in ready ranch on 2 acres with finished basement! Recently updated with new carpet, refinished hardwood floors in the kitchen, and fresh paint throughout the main level. Only 20 minutes from NGIC, 10 minutes from Ruckersville (Lowes, Wallmart, Starbucks) and other restaurants. It's less than 25 minutes to Hollymead Town Center (Target, Harris Teeter) and CHO Airport. Featuring 3 bedrooms on the main level, and a huge rec room in the basement; perfect for a hangout space, a movie room, or guest space. The attached garage is oversized for plenty of storage and work space. There's plenty of natural light in the living room and kitchen thanks to vaulted ceilings. Winters will be cozy with two fireplaces, and enjoy your morning coffee on the back deck taking in the wooded views. The HOA gives you access to Lake Greene where you can kayak, fish, or just relax. Open house Saturday 6th 2-4pm!
